  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "1.Requirement Analysis"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_9-59-36.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_9-59-36.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "According to the user manual, to perform a plausibility check of the Vref voltage of the EVADC, the internal"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Vddk of the EVADC can be used to verify the plausibility of the Vref voltage. Vddk is sampled by the voltage"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "configured on GxCH29, and GxCH29 can be mapped to GxCH0 of any EVADC hardware unit. That is, the voltage"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "sampling value of Vddk can be read from the result register of GxCH0 (if configured correctly)."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "user manual information interpretation"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-5-35.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-5-35.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-6-24.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-6-24.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "By configuring Alias register in CH0/CH1.The Alias feature allows the user to redirect conversion requests for"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "channels 0 and/or 1 to other channel numbers. Using the alias feature, a conversion request for channel 0 or"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "channel 1 leads to a conversion of the analog input channel “x” instead of channel 0 or channel 1. To use CH29"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "(Vddk reference signal) for channel 0 or 1 simply setGxALIAS.ALIAS0/1=29 and the successive conversion"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "result on Ch0/1 will contain the Vddk signal level. Channel configuration and result register assignment are"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "chosen in GxCHCTR0/1 (Channel Control Registers)."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-8-37.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-8-37.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-8-54.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-8-54.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-9-6.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-9-6.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "2.Function Implementation-Mcal Configuration"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-10-1.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-10-1.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-10-14.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
