    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-36-38.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-36-38.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "3.Function Implementation-Coding"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20implement%20TC3xx%20EVADC%20reference%20plausibility%20check%20using%20VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-11-28.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to implement TC3xx EVADC reference plausibility check using VDDK/image-2026-1-16_10-11-28.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After mapping the VDDK voltage sampling to GxCHy using EB configuration, the VDDK voltage sampling value can be read in"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "the result register of GxCHy."
    }
  ],
